VALUES
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00783', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '假定全體商業銀行資產負債表中，負債包括500億元的存款以及向中央銀行借款100億元，而資產包括 150億元的政府債券以及放款300億元。若法定存款準備率為20%，則下列敘述何者正確？', '["商業銀行同業間放款利率高於重貼現率，因此超額準備為50億元", "商業銀行同業間放款利率低於重貼現率，因此超額準備為50億元", "商業銀行同業間放款利率等於重貼現率，因此超額準備為0億元", "商業銀行同業間放款利率等於重貼現率，因此超額準備為50億元"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00784', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者並非中央銀行的工作內容？', '["向立法院報告臺灣銀行與中央信託局的合併案", "某商銀短期資金不足，其負責人請求給予資金融通", "與外商銀行負責人喝咖啡，並研討新臺幣匯率走勢", "與七大行庫代表開會檢討近期資金情勢"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00785', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當中央銀行在公開市場賣出所持有的100億元的政府債券時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["貨幣基數與全體商業銀行準備金皆同時減少100億元", "貨幣基數減少100億元，全體商業銀行準備金可能會減少", "貨幣基數減少100億元，全體商業銀行準備金不受影響", "貨幣基數不受影響，全體商業銀行準備金減少100億元"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00786', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在封閉體系並且考慮政府部門下，政府以定額稅方式課稅，假設邊際消費傾向為0.8，政府購買增加1,000 萬元並且完全以定額稅融通，則均衡產出：', '["增加800萬元", "增加1,000萬元", "增加5,000萬元", "增加200萬元"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00787', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列是一簡單凱因斯模型： 消費：C＝95+0.8(Y－T) 投資：I＝32+0.03Y 稅收：T＝62+0.1Y 請問這個經濟體系的政府支出乘數為多少？', '["4", "5", "6", "7"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00788', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當政府的預算有赤字時，可以透過下列何種方法改善赤字？', '["減少稅收", "增加開支", "擴大政府投資", "提高所得稅率"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00789', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國憲法第23條規定：「以上各條列舉之自由權利，除為防止妨害他人自由、避免緊急危難、維持社會', '["比例原則", "法律保留原則", "誠實信用原則", "信賴保護原則"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00790', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '1989 年國小老師李幸長發起「無殼蝸牛運動」，夜宿臺北市忠孝東路，抗議政府漠視人民的居住權益。 後來，無住屋運動轉型為「崔媽媽基金會」，透過協助弱勢族群解決租屋問題，落實「居者適其屋」的 理念。關於「無殼蝸牛運動」發展到「崔媽媽基金會」之成立，下列敘述何者正確？', '["由非營利組織轉型為營利組織", "原強調利他主義後轉為主張利己導向", "原以公益為使命後轉為重視成本效益", "從倡議的社會運動轉為成立服務性的社團"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00791', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '近年來雙薪家庭比例上升，由於父母忙於工作，因此托兒所、安親班等機構成為安置孩童的重要處所。 根據統計，臺灣目前有政府立案的各種安親班、補習班、才藝班數量遠遠超過全臺超商數量。此現象說 明隨著社會變遷，家庭的何種功能正在轉變？', '["生育功能", "經濟功能", "社會化功能", "傳遞社會地位"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00792', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '所謂「友善職場」，就是無歧視、重平等的職場。在職場中，勞工與雇主彼此尊重、合作，共同打造一 個性別平權的工作環境。下列何種作法，最有助於促進「友善職場」？', '["開放同志勞工因伴侶生病時可請家庭照顧假", "營造玻璃天花板環境以便落實性別實質平等", "健全性別職業隔離制度以保障女性就業機會", "降低女性勞動參與率以避免蠟燭兩頭燒現象"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "57e6993d4375", "answer_pdf_sha1": "215bbf5687be", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
